{"lemma":"عَوارٌ","slug":"عَوارٌ","root":"ع.#.ر","root_slug":"ع-_-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-_-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n30986","n30987","n30988","n30991"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"fault, flaw, defect, crevasse"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"martin (certain birds in the family Hirundinidae)"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ع و ر (ʕ w r), related to ideas of missing one eye or having a lacuna.\n\nApparently a corruption of عُوَّاذ (ʕuwwāḏ) from the root ع و ذ (ʕ w ḏ), related to taking refuge."},"ipa":["/ʕa.waːr/","/ʕuw.waːr/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30986","headword_ar":"عَوَارٌ","root":"Ewr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuwaArN","text_ar":"عُوَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiwaArN","text_ar":"عِوَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A fault; a defect; an imperfection; a blemish; something amiss;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K;) in an article of merchandise, (S, Mgh, Msb,) and in a garment, or piece of cloth, (TA,) and in a slave, (Msb,) and in a beast: (TA:) or in a garment, or piece of cloth,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hole,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a rent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, Mgh, Msb, K, TA;) and so in the like, and in a house or tent and the like; (TA;) and in a garment, or piece of cloth, also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a burn;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a rottenness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) and some say that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawaArN","text_ar":"عَوَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with fet-h, is only in goods, or commodities, or articles of merchandise. (Msb.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siloEapN *aAtu EawaArK","text_ar":"سِلْعَةٌ ذَاتُ عَوَارٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuwaArK","text_ar":"عُوَارٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to AZ,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An article of merchandise having a fault,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawarN","text_ar":"عَوَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","AZ","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n30987","headword_ar":"عُوَارٌ","root":"Ewr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawaArN","text_ar":"عَوَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n30988","headword_ar":"عِوَارٌ","root":"Ewr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawaArN","text_ar":"عَوَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n30991","headword_ar":"عُوَّارٌ","root":"Ewr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAy^irN","text_ar":"عَايِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}